\newlabel{tab:attacks}{{11}{37}{Category-level attack outcomes by system (110 attempts each: 3 spoof, 4 replay, 3 substitution, 1 escalation, $\times $ 10 repeats). The bypass rate measures the fraction of attempts that succeeded in circumventing the intended control. The user-space bypass rates reflect deliberate per-category instrumented weakening of the mediator and do not represent the performance of a fully hardened user-space implementation}{table.11}{}}
